Name: Bunny Memory
About the game: The astronaut bunny sent on a journey wandered in space for so long that they completely forgot everything. Collect memory points and train your memory, helping the bunny unlock fragments of memories. Features: 3 card types: numbers, letters and pictures with bunnies 5 difficulties cooperative mode for 2 players split-screen mode for 2 players (requires 2 gamepads)
